Job Description
AN ISO-CERTIFIED LEADING CONSTRUCTION COMPANY, BASED IN DUBAI, INVITES QUALIFIED AND UAE EXPERIENCED CANDIDATES FOR THE FOLLOWING POSITIONS:
- Project Engineers (7-10 years exp.) Reference: PE
- Site Engineers (5-6 years exp.) Reference: SE
