- MEP Cost Control Engineers (5-6 years exp.) Reference: MEP (CE)
- MEP Procurement Engineer (5-8 years exp.) Reference: PRE
- MEP QA/QC Engineer (Plant) (5-6 years exp.) Reference: MEP (QAQC)
- Material Engineer (5-6 years exp.) Reference: ME
- Electrical Engineers (5-6 years exp.) Reference: EE
- Mechanical Engineers (5-6 years exp.) Reference: ME
- Procurement Officers (Min. 5 years exp.) Reference: PO
